---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Sunset Guardian
description: Practical financial tools and clear explanations that make complicated numbers easier to understand.
---

<section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">
        Practical tools. Clear explanations.
    </p>

    <h1>
        Make financial numbers easier to understand.
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-copy">
        Fast, straightforward calculators and guides designed
        to turn confusing financial concepts into useful answers.
    </p>

    <div class="actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/tools/cagr/">
            Try the CAGR Calculator
        </a>

        <a class="button button-secondary" href="/tools/">
            Browse all tools
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<section
    class="feature-card"
    aria-labelledby="featured-tool-title"
>
    <div class="feature-card-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">
            Featured tool
        </p>

        <h2 id="featured-tool-title">
            CAGR Calculator
        </h2>

        <p>
            Calculate the constant annual growth rate that turns
            a starting value into an ending value over a selected
            number of years.
        </p>

        <p>
            The calculator also shows total return, updates instantly,
            and requires no account or login.
        </p>

        <a class="inline-link" href="/tools/cagr/">
            Open the CAGR Calculator →
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="metric-card" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Example CAGR</span>
        <strong>8.45%</strong>
        <small>
            $10,000 → $15,000 over 5 years
        </small>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Available tools</h2>

        <p>
            Each published tool is added here automatically.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
        {% for tool in collections.tools %}
            <a class="link-card" href="{{ tool.url }}">
                <h3>{{ tool.data.title }}</h3>

                <p>
                    {{ tool.data.description }}
                </p>

                <span>Open tool →</span>
            </a>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</section>
